info.author: Paulo Radatz, Ênio Viana, Rodolfo Londero
info.name: py-dss-interface
info.summary: The py-dss-interface is a Python package that provides a Python interface to the OFFICIAL version of OpenDSS (Open-source Distribution System Simulator) software. OpenDSS is a free, open-source software for simulating and analyzing power distribution systems.
